c: 12
v: 80
t: "They failed to convince Yusuf, and consulted each other. The oldest brother said (to others), \"Do you not know? Father had obtained a firm oath upon Allah from you. And earlier, in Yusuf´s case, you had been neglectful. I will not leave this place until my father permits me, or until Allah decides my fate. He is the Best of the judges"